{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7f0ea9b0e9","title":"对攻击大陈港敌舰方案的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"54de06926e","index":0,"year":1954,"month":7,"day":24,"articleId":"7f0ea9b0e9"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"27136b46f8","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"7f0ea9b0e9","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"德怀，即彭德怀，当时任人民革命军事委员会副主席。克诚，即黄克诚，当时任中国人民解放军副总参谋长兼总后勤部部长。"},{"id":"f4c5b9e10a","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"7f0ea9b0e9","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指华东海军司令部1954年7月21日关于攻击大陈港敌舰的方案给海军司令部的电报。方案提出空军和水面舰艇联合打击，单兵种寻机打击和布雷相结合，并说为了做好联合打击的协同，需3周至1个月的准备时间。"}],"contents":[{"id":"ceb0b8a967","type":"title","text":"对攻击大陈港敌舰方案的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"7f0ea9b0e9"},{"id":"27136b46f8","type":"paragraph","text":"德怀、克诚同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"7f0ea9b0e9"},{"id":"f4c5b9e10a","type":"paragraph","text":"请考虑是否须调华东军区，福建、浙江、上海三军区的负责人客一人来京讨论此问题。此电内所提开天准备时间是必要的，必要时还可延长至四十天。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"7f0ea9b0e9"},{"id":"fc514886ac","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"7f0ea9b0e9"},{"id":"8be7369d9f","type":"paragraph","text":"七月廿四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"7f0ea9b0e9"}],"page":{"id":"eaa8ef86d4","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"7f0ea9b0e9","start":172,"end":172}}}},"__N_SSG":true}